<br>
BUT<br>
<br>
The mobs don't chain-heal as much any more.  I'd gladly eat Yet Another 500pt DD than to have to tank a 5000HP mob down to 200HPs again.<br>
<br>
The key thing is that if you pull a caster, you must get out of it's line-of-sight quick, or he'll just chain cast on you.<br>
